    {
        "id":"undertell_marked_stone_warning_1",
        "message":"The pull of the mark is becoming harder to ignore. A sudden wave of dizziness washes over you, and the whispers grow louder. They speak of danger, of a life lost if you do not return.\nYou must turn back...the time is running out. Crossglen calls. You cannot linger here.",
