    },
    {
        "id":"undertell_marked_stone_warning_2",
        "message":"Your steps grow heavier, the air thick with oppressive energy. The pull within your chest tightens, and the whispers now sound desperate, almost frantic.\nReturn to Crossglen... You cannot stay here. Your father's life is in peril. Do not test fate any longer!",
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"galmore_nondisplayed",
                "value":2
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"undertell_marked_stone_warning_3",
        "message":"You feel your breath catch in your throat, the world around you warping and twisting. The mark is burning, a cold fire coursing through your veins, clawing at your very soul.\nTURN BACK NOW! Crossglen is in danger. You are too far from what matters. Return at once\u2014before it is too late!"
    },
