    {
        "id":"undertell_marked_stone_leta_30",
        "message":"Strange? Who does he think he is, meddling in my life? I'm fine! Just...leave me alone!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"You don't seem fine. You've been pacing, muttering to yourself. Something isn't right.",
