    {
        "id":"undertell_marked_stone_leta_40",
        "message":"[voice trembling but defensive] Not right? Not right! What would you know about it? You don't know what I've seen, what I've felt!\n[Leta pauses, clutching her head as if in pain.]",
        "replies":[
